products.title: Country Blossom Ashen Gold Roller Blind
products.description: This sweet country blossom ashen gold roller blind has a lovely scandi vibe to it, a palette of grey white and yellow decorating a simple floral design. We particularly love the pared back nature of this blind, nothing more than a few lines and shapes, which when brought all to this sweet country blossom ashen gold roller blind has a lovely scandi vibe to it, a palette of grey white and yellow decorating a simple floral design.
